Title: logwatch patterns: now able to set a rule which converts on incoming state to another
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.4.0i1
Date: 1475521109
Class: feature

The WATO rule now allows you to configure a complete state conversion.
For example, you can set that all reported <i>C</i> lines are converted to <i>W</i>.

